{"tid":1549111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［和你塞］有時事實係需要接受","createTime":"2019-09-07T08:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T11:49:45.000Z","uid":158159,"like":355,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"2a219d25ed483fa70f80c65f6a5f998b20b739d9","tid":1549111,"uid":158159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"唔係每次話失敗就係失敗散水撚<br />\n今次唔成功係事實<br />\n狗每架巴士都上去查 但查5分鐘就放行<br />\n根本唔構成「塞」<br />\n唔存在「POPO自己已經塞咗青馬」<br />\n成條公路極少車 巴士極少人<br />\n<br />\n今日行動缺乏共識同計劃<br />\n又有好多人因為上個禮拜而唔敢出<br />\n雖然唔指責 但知道衰喺邊好重要<br />\n<br />\n聽日美領見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/deNK5RZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdeNK5RZ.jpg&h=e9b0e860&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"599946d3e302d3a22a2fec0e442f1a254b3a897a","tid":1549111,"uid":94538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:16:22.000Z","msg":"[人在機場 個人意見] 塞香港站+阻人入青馬就夠<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548911</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7c07ce23a8b1d510a8263fcf29a38ec24ecae7f8","tid":1549111,"uid":76702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:16:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"961f545dc8c3dd2857d99535866e3fc66c540b1f","tid":1549111,"uid":30966,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:17:27.000Z","msg":"Agger 聽日見啦"},{"pid":"d9ebf2edb33a10d63b67ff91d00363a7b396dafc","tid":1549111,"uid":34334,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8f7b694d1469bc1fe1eea4e50d96d07998bb605","tid":1549111,"uid":65024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8411b24143956ac175b45591b0a88b8225d3